column2:
"Such powerful foes, defeated in an instant...
Now we can push them back!"
"You can't be so reckless out here. Didn't somebody once tell me selfish actions get you kicked out of ARKS?"
"Of course I did. That's why I came here to help."
"Sorry you had to come all the way out here! I've got another favor to ask!"
"Me and the math genius have got the city covered, but they're swarming the school too!"
"Itsuki's right. You've shown us how to eliminate them."
"There are still people who need to be rescued. Please go to them."
"...I know you two act tough, but these are dangerous foes even for the ARKS. Take this chance to flee."
"What are you saying, Suzuki? We faced Dark Falz together, didn't we?"
"Rina's right. So long as I can help, I won't back down."
"...Let's go! We'll protect this planet... We'll protect the Earth!"
